{"tid":2510792,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"［移民潮］港元存款3月流失1400億元","createTime":"2021-04-30T11:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T12:25:00.000Z","uid":24730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ea235a3baca7c1a00fa6a2884a1d6fb6feaf6496","tid":2510792,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"港元存款3月流失1400億元 <br />\n<br />\n金管局統計數字顯示，撇除新股認購貸款所產生的存款，3月份認可機構的存款總額及港元存款分別下跌0.2%及0.4%。首季計，存款總額及港元存款分別上升1.2%及2.7%，若撇除新股因素，則分別上升0.9%及2.1%。<br />\n<br />\n隨新股認購活動完結及發行人退回認購資金，3月份存款總額按月下跌1%，其中港元存款下跌1.8%至7.5萬億元，活期存款按月跌一成，至1.52萬億元；外幣存款則沒有明顯變動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人民幣存款按月上升1.5%，於3月底為7,725億元人民幣；跨境貿易結算的人民幣匯款總額於3月份為6,764億元人民幣，而2月份的數字為4,411億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該局指出，存款變動受多項因素影響，包括利率走勢、市場集資活動等，較適宜觀察較長期趨勢，毋須過度解讀個別月份的波動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3月份貸款與墊款總額則按月下跌0.4%，撇除新股認購貸款，貸款總額則升0.7%。其中在香港使用的貸款（包括貿易融資）較2月下跌0.6%，在香港境外使用的貸款則按月微升0.1%。由於港元存款跌幅較港元貸款大，港元貸存比率由2月底的82.8%，上升至3月底的83.3%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3月港元貨幣供應量M2及M3皆下跌1.8%，分別為8.12萬億元及8.14萬億元，按年比較則分別上升9.2%及9.1%。3月份經季節因素調整的港元貨幣供應量M1下跌3.6%，至2.03萬億元，按年則上升27.5%，部份反映投資相關活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210430/EGFOW67Z6ZHIVIYMIM7AZNZBCU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210430%2FEGFOW67Z6ZHIVIYMIM7AZNZBCU%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=e0e9dafe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210430%2FEGFOW67Z6ZHIVIYMIM7AZNZBCU%2F&h=9d2bb6a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210430/EGFOW67Z6ZHIVIYMIM7AZNZBCU/</a>"},{"pid":"923d304beae1655eaae8c0fb35f310c4cf56b956","tid":2510792,"uid":162268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"政府冇錢咪加稅<br />\n再立法充公財產<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71fac8dbe0e2411c93ac396cbd188205ffc6985","tid":2510792,"uid":261819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT5TW1jcaZc6hHzp9Nw3o1bUApXza9Ts7yqScksjdAPZd?filename=EM1uGMY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEM1uGMY.jpg&h=732e482f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ec4eab7e5675243b47b96e179306b77a9845e51","tid":2510792,"uid":144275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:17:17.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首季計，存款總額及港元存款分別上升1.2%及2.7%，若撇除新股因素，則分別上升0.9%及2.1%。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e55ebbc3e6454c3c1e73b9bf463257919879ba6","tid":2510792,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:19:05.000Z","msg":"攞晒買樓啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584cc0eda377497938b5c28446f88442d06d8a4f","tid":2510792,"uid":329550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ec4eab7e5675243b47b96e179306b77a9845e51","tid":2510792,"uid":144275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:17:17.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首季計，存款總額及港元存款分別上升1.2%及2.7%，若撇除新股因素，則分別上升0.9%及2.1%。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:21:32.000Z","msg":"你咁踢爆樓豬，又會比人追擊話係五毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dacf44ac5492514f2384eedc9bcd3e2ada025f7","tid":2510792,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e55ebbc3e6454c3c1e73b9bf463257919879ba6","tid":2510792,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:19:05.000Z","msg":"攞晒買樓啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:23:19.000Z","msg":"咪係 藏富於民就係靠樓"},{"pid":"3faadb4855beb91780159262a0effde7b7c42001","tid":2510792,"uid":9541,"lik